@startuml AI_Recommendation
title AI Recommendation Flow

note over Merchant, Groq
  PLANNED — This module is not yet implemented.
  The flow below describes the intended design.
end note

actor "Merchant" as Merchant
participant "Merchant Dashboard\n(Next.js)" as UI
participant "AI Recommendation\nService (Spring Boot)" as AIS
participant "Store Service" as SS
participant "Product Service" as PS
participant "PostgreSQL DB" as DB
participant "Groq API" as Groq

== Request AI Recommendations ==

Merchant -> UI : Click "Get AI Recommendations"\non dashboard
UI -> AIS : POST /ai/recommendations/generate\n{storeId} + Bearer Token

AIS -> AIS : Validate merchant owns\nthis storeId

== Collect Store Data ==

AIS -> SS : GET store layout & design config\n{theme, colors, banner, navigation structure}
SS -> DB : Query store configuration
DB --> SS : Return store config
SS --> AIS : Store layout & design data

AIS -> PS : GET product catalog snapshot\n{storeId}
PS -> DB : Query products\n{name, description, images,\nprice, category, stock}
DB --> PS : Return products
PS --> AIS : Product list

== Check Rate Limit ==

AIS -> DB : Fetch last recommendation\ntimestamp for this store
DB --> AIS : Last generated: {date}

note over AIS
  Rate limit: max 1 request per hour
  per store to control Groq API costs
end note

alt Too soon since last request
    AIS --> UI : 429 Too Many Requests\n"Please wait before generating\nnew recommendations"
    UI --> Merchant : Show cooldown message
else Proceed

    == Build AI Prompt ==

    AIS -> AIS : Build structured prompt\n{storeLayout, theme, products,\ninstructions}

    == Call Groq API ==

    AIS -> Groq : POST /openai/v1/chat/completions\n{model: llama3-70b,\n messages: [system + user prompt],\n response_format: JSON}

    alt Groq API unavailable / timeout
        Groq --> AIS : 503 / timeout error
        AIS --> UI : 502 Bad Gateway\n"AI service temporarily unavailable"
        UI --> Merchant : Show error message

    else Groq responds successfully
        Groq --> AIS : JSON recommendations array\n[{category, issue, recommendation, priority}]

        AIS -> AIS : Parse & validate JSON response
        AIS -> DB : Save recommendations\n{storeId, generatedAt, recommendations}
        DB --> AIS : Saved with recommendationBatchId

        AIS --> UI : 200 OK\n{batchId, recommendations}

        UI --> Merchant : Render recommendations panel\ngrouped by priority (High / Medium / Low)

        loop For each recommendation
            Merchant -> UI : Click Accept / Reject / Ignore

            alt Accepted or Rejected
                UI -> AIS : PATCH /ai/recommendations/{id}\n{status: ACCEPTED | REJECTED}
                AIS -> DB : Update status
                AIS --> UI : Confirmed
            end
        end

        == View Recommendation History ==

        Merchant -> UI : Click "View Past Recommendations"
        UI -> AIS : GET /ai/recommendations/history\n{storeId, page, limit}
        AIS -> DB : Query all recommendation batches
        DB --> AIS : Return history
        AIS --> UI : Paginated history list
        UI --> Merchant : Show history with status per recommendation
    end
end

@enduml
